========================================
üß± BLOCK 1 ‚Äî SHELL
========================================
Title: Cave Runner
Short Description:
    Side-scrolling endless runner where the player avoids hazards
    and collects shards for score.

Goal:
    Stay alive as long as possible and achieve a high score.

========================================
üéÆ BLOCK 2 ‚Äî GAME LOOP / BEHAVIOR
========================================
On Start:
    - Spawn player at left side of screen.
    - Initialize score and difficulty level 1.
    - Start background scroll.

On Input:
    - SPACE / TAP: Player jumps.
    - Longer press = slightly higher jump (optional).

On Update (each frame / tick):
    - Move player forward at SPEED_BASE, increasing over time.
    - Spawn obstacles at SPAWN_RATE with random gaps.
    - Detect collisions: if player hits obstacle ‚Üí trigger GAME OVER.
    - Increase difficulty every DIFFICULTY_INTERVAL seconds.

On Game Over:
    - Stop movement.
    - Show GAME_OVER_TEXT and final score.
    - Offer RESTART_BUTTON_TEXT.

========================================
üñçÔ∏è BLOCK 3 ‚Äî TUNING KNOBS
========================================
# These values are SAFE for humans to tweak.

SPEED_BASE:             6.0      # starting horizontal speed
SPEED_INCREMENT:        0.4      # speed ramp per difficulty step
GRAVITY:                32.0     # downward force on jumps
JUMP_FORCE:             16.0     # base jump push
SPAWN_RATE:             1.2      # seconds between obstacle spawns
DIFFICULTY_INTERVAL:    20.0     # seconds until difficulty increases
MAX_LIVES:              1        # classic arcade: 1 life per run

========================================
üåê BLOCK 4 ‚Äî PUBLIC TEXT
========================================
TITLE_TEXT:             "Cave Runner"
START_MESSAGE:          "Tap or press SPACE to jump."
GAME_OVER_TEXT:         "You fell. Try again."
SCORE_LABEL:            "Score"
HIGH_SCORE_LABEL:       "High Score"
RESTART_BUTTON_TEXT:    "Run Again"

========================================
üìù BLOCK 5 ‚Äî HUMAN NOTES
========================================
- Visual ideas:
    - Dark cave background, subtle parallax.
    - Player is a small explorer with a lantern.

- Sound ideas:
    - Low rumble ambience.
    - Soft chime when collecting shards.

- Future expansions:
    - Power-ups (double jump, slow motion).
    - New biomes as difficulty rises.
